				<span class="finalNameCheck">이름은 필수 입력 사항입니다.</span>
				<br>
				<p style="margin: 20px 0 10px 0;">닉네임</p>
				<input type="text" class="nickname" name="nickname" id="textbox" value="${member2.nickname}">
				<span class="finalNicknameCheck">닉네임은 필수 입력 사항입니다.</span>
				<span class="nicknameCheck1">사용 가능한 닉네임입니다.</span>
	   			<span class="nicknameCheck2">이미 사용 중인 닉네임입니다.</span>
				<br>
				<p style="margin: 20px 0 10px 0;">전화번호</p>
				<input type="text" class="phone" name="phone" value="${member2.phone}" id="textbox">
				<span class="finalPhoneCheck">전화번호는 필수 입력 사항입니다.</span>
				<br>
			    <p style="margin: 20px 0 10px 0;">이메일</p>
				<input type="text" class="email" name="email" id="textbox" value="${member2.email}">
				<span class="finalEmailCheck">이메일은 필수 입력 사항입니다.</span>
				<br>
			    <p style="margin: 20px 0 10px 0;">우편번호</p>
			    <div class="addressBox">
				<input type="text" class="zipCode" name="zipCode" id="textbox" value="${member2.zipCode}">
				<input type="button" value="주소 찾기" onclick="executionDaumAddress()" id="overlap">
				</div>
				<br>
			    <p style="margin: 20px 0 10px 0;">주소</p>
				<input type="text" class="addressRoad" name="addressRoad" id="textbox" value="${member2.addressRoad}">
				<br>
			    <p style="margin: 20px 0 10px 0;">상세 주소</p>
				<input type="text" class="addressDetail" name="addressDetail" id="textbox" value="${member2.addressDetail}">
				<span class="finalAddressCheck">상세 주소는 필수 입력 사항입니다.</span>
				<br>
			    <p style="margin: 20px 0 10px 0;">포인트</p>
				<input type="text" class="point" name="point" id="textbox" value="${member2.point}">
				<span class="finalPointCheck">포인트를 입력해 주세요.</span>
				<br>
				<div id="radio">
